title: on me by section 1(2) of the Criminal Justice (Smuggling of Persons) Act 2021
heading: 2. The 31st day of December 2021 is appointed as the day on which the
text_raw:
2. The 31st day of December 2021 is appointed as the day on which the 
Criminal Justice (Smuggling of Persons) Act 2021 (No. 42 of 2021) comes into 
operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

30 December, 2021. 

HELEN MCENTEE, 
Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 11th January, 2022.
